                            <comment id="14509939" author="srowen" created="Thu, 23 Apr 2015 22:13:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like the check needs to be expanded. To this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;require(rdds.flatMap(_.partitioner).toSet.size == 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;add before:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;require(rdds.count(_.partitioner.isDefined) == rdds.size)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think. Want to try a PR?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
